subtitleNullable: State wise Energy requirement in India from 2015 to 2022
descriptionNullable: India's monthly energy needs from 2015 until 2022. The energy requirement is in Mega units. The number for the whole of India will be different when the grand total is calculated because this dataset comprises the energy requirements for all Indian states, including union territories except Delhi.
